    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/116407229\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"Fresh Road Fresh Visitors\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>A Malibu classic has been getting repaved lately. This new section got a beautiful layer of blacktop that’s smooth as butter. A fresh group of visitors from Ohio and Quebec filmed a tight pack run to break it the fresh pavement.<br>\nFilm/Edit: Alex Ameen<br>\nMusic: “California Dreamin'” -Eddie Hazel<br>\nSkaters: Alexis Labrecque, Avery Wilcox, Alex Colorito, Dan Wilczek</p>",
