    "pageTitle": "James Kelly",
    "postDate": "2012-07-16",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/4267466460/sizes/l/\"><img src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/james-kelly/4267466460_f7ea5d86fb_b.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br>\nStalefish slide through a hairpin. James just flows.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/4266704971/sizes/l/\"><img src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/james-kelly/4266704971_aa909b5f88_b.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br>\nJames’s standup slides go both ways.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/4267460112/sizes/l/\"><img src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/james-kelly/4267460112_2050e1e165_b.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br>\nSwitch!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/4266726687/sizes/l/\"><img src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/james-kelly/4266726687_466f38405f_b.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br>\nLow-down back 360 through a big steep righty. Does that count as a 540?</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/4222106571/sizes/l/\"><img src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/james-kelly/4222106571_66811b3374_b.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br>\nThat’s not from foot-braking.</p>\n<p>James’s lifestyle is made possible by <a title=\"Loaded Boards\" href=\"https://www.loadedboards.com\" target=\"_blank\">Loaded Boards</a>, <a title=\"Orangatang Wheels\" href=\"https://www.Orangatangwheels.com\" target=\"_blank\">Orangatang Wheels</a>, and <a title=\"Randal Trucks\" href=\"https://www.randal.com\" target=\"_blank\">Randal Trucks</a>.</p>",
