    "pageTitle": "Local Adam Colton",
    "postDate": "2012-03-13",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p>Adam Colton is well known for his boardwalking skills as well as his  ability to push his skateboard unreasonably long distances.  What some  people don’t know is that he also kills it in the hills.&nbsp; He claims his  secret is a well balanced diet and pooping at least five times daily.    Adam gets help from <a href=\"https://www.loadedboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Loaded Boards</a> and <a href=\"https://www.orangatangwheels.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Orangatang Wheels</a>.</p>",
