    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/10854418\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Pack riding on live roads can lead to some hairy situations. Don’t push  your limits into blind turns and prepare for the unexpected by giving  yourself ample space between riders so you have time to react. Special  thanks to Justin Rouleau for sending this carnage over. Please stay on  your board and in your lane when riding with traffic!</p>",
