    "pageTitle": "Santa Gnarbara Outlaw 2012",
    "postDate": "2013-04-14",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<div id=\"watch-description-text\">\n<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wi9d9ZN267s?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“Here is some footage of the 2012 Santa  Gnarbara Outlaw Race.  The race went really well and to everyones relief  it was able to finish without getting shut down.  All in all everyone  had a super fun time racing, waiting for burgers, and watching the  competitors.  We had 1 podium finish for Niran in 3rd place.  Sid  finished 4th and Justin got eliminated in the semi finals.  Isaiah was  filming due to a recent knee surgery.  We had a super fun time and can’t  wait for next year!</p>\n<p>Grom Podium:<br>\n1st place: Sean Chantarachara<br>\n2nd place: Sammy Parks<br>\n3rd place: Nathaniel Hodson</p>\n<p>Open Podium:<br>\n1st: Tim Del Rosario<br>\n2nd: Max Myers<br>\n3rd: Dustin Hampton</p>\n<p>Filmed and Edited by Isaiah Brothers</p>\n<p>Song: Up Around The Bend by Creedence Clearwater Revival</p>\n<p>Setups: Ha!<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.longneckgiraffeproductions.net/\" target=\"_blank\"><br>\nLong Neck Giraffe Productions</a></p>\n<p>LNGP”</p>\n</div>",
