    "pageTitle": "Skatesgiving: Jungle",
    "postDate": "2011-01-19",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/84172191\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>We revisted a Classic on <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/skatesgiving\" target=\"_blank\">Skatesgiving</a> this past trip. <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/12/29/2011/skatesgiving-jungle-raw-run\" target=\"_blank\">Jungle</a> was found over half a decade <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0-FwxwxC47g\" target=\"_blank\">ago</a>. This year’s sponsors are <a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz Skateboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9 Skateboards</a>, Kebbek Skateboards, <a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/home/\" target=\"_blank\">Comet Skateboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.RayneLongboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rayne Longboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.paristruckco.com\" target=\"_blank\">Paris Truck Co</a>, <a href=\"https://radesigns.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RAD Wheels</a>, &amp; Bear Trucks.</p>",
