    "pageTitle": "Rumble at the Ranch – Round 3 Heats 2-3",
    "postDate": "2013-12-15",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p>The heats at the <a href=\"https://www.rumbleattheranch.com\" target=\"_blank\">Rumble</a> just keep getting better&nbsp;and better, who is going to take it all!? Be sure to tune in on Monday for a SkateHouse exclusive look at&nbsp;the Louis vs. AJ&nbsp;race!</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/116780171\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"Rumble At The Ranch: Round 3 Heat 2\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>Round 3, heat 2:&nbsp;</strong>Jimmy Riha vs. Ali Nas</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/116781982\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"Rumble At The Ranch: Round 3 Heat 3\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>Round 3, heat 3:&nbsp;</strong>Louis Pilloni vs. AJ Haiby</p>",
