    "postDate": "2013-11-24",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p>In this last heat of round 3, Micah Green squares up with Zak Maytum and we learn who is <a href=\"https://www.rumbleattheranch.com/rumble-at-the-ranch-downhill-heats/\" target=\"_blank\">moving on to the semi-finals</a>.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/116785181\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"Rumble At The Ranch: Round 3 Heat 4\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>",
