    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/vrWDCGpd4Ho\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.muirskate.com\">Muirskate</a> Ryan Ricker and Derek Smith headed out to King of Kona this year ready for a fun-filled weekend. The Team ran into Tom Weiss with <a href=\"https://originalskateboards.com\">Original Skateboards</a> at the airport and knew this was the guy to keep an eye on.</p>",
