    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/86095035\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>This year’s Soldiers of Downhill was dominated by the <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/skatesgiving\" target=\"_blank\">Skatesgiving</a> crew. Big thanks to our sponsors; <a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz Skateboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9 Skateboards</a>, Kebbek Skateboards, <a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/home/\" target=\"_blank\">Comet Skateboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.RayneLongboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rayne Longboards</a>, Paris Truck Co, <a href=\"https://radesigns.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RAD Wheels</a>, &amp; Bear Trucks.</p>\n<p>1st: <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/george-mackenzie\" target=\"_blank\">George Mackenzie</a><br>\n2nd: <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/max-wippermann\" target=\"_blank\">Max Wippermann</a><br>\n3rd: <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/matt-kienzle\" target=\"_blank\">Matt Kienzle</a><br>\n4th: <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/louis-pilloni\" target=\"_blank\">Louis Pilloni</a></p>",
