    "pageTitle": "Road Trip: BDA does Boulder",
    "postDate": "2016-08-28",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/120447085?color=9e0000&amp;title=0&amp;byline=0\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Bad Decisions Alex had been keeping his eye on Boulder, Colorado for a while. Good skating, cheap drinks, and college girls made it a tempting film location. After seeing that winter had passed and it was 60º and sunny every day he booked his plane ticket to visit Boulder Skate Mansion. Naturally the snow started pouring down the second his plane landed. Regardless he managed to have a blast partying with Garrett Creamer, snow skating with Ethan Galaif, skating with Aaron Hampshire and some of the locals, and watching Comet’s <a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/\">Nick Ketner</a> destroy the local skatepark.</p>",
