    "pageTitle": "Session: Three Amigos",
    "postDate": "2017-03-08",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p>Sometimes you got to put the call out to get the session rolling. Oscar Gutiereez (<a href=\"https://www.sector9.com\" target=\"_blank\">S9</a>, <a href=\"https://www.radesigns.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RAD</a>, Bear, Tree) sends a call into the wind to form a trio of amigos with Daniel Luna (<a href=\"https://www.sector9.com\" target=\"_blank\">S9</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gullwingtruckco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">GW</a>, <a href=\"https://www.muirskate.com\" target=\"_blank\">Muir</a>) and AJ Haiby&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://www.sector9.com\" target=\"_blank\">S9</a>, <a href=\"https://www.gullwingtruckco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">GW</a>, <a href=\"https://www.muirskate.com\" target=\"_blank\">Muir</a>) to session a local San Diego spot. Special thanks to <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/12/02/2014/raw-run-puebla-oscar-gutierrez-brian-sandoval\" target=\"_blank\">Brian Sandoval</a> for helping make the film session happen.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
