    "pageTitle": "Housemates: A Loveletter",
    "postDate": "2018-03-12",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p>Dexter Manning (<a href=\"https://landyachtz.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz</a>), Austin Pedroni (<a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Arbor</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/wheels/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Sucrose</a>), &amp; Eric Mroz (<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mrozphotography/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">MrozPhotography</a>) drove south from the Skate Mansion to meet up with SHM Co-founder <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/tags/louis-pilloni\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Louis Pilloni</a>. Any session at <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/?s=angie%27s+curves\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Angie’s Curves</a> is good, but some are better than others. </p>",
