    "pageTitle": "How the hell does Louis do that? | SkateHouseMedia.com",
    "postDate": "2013-11-04",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/6836616032/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/how-the-hell-does-louis-do-that-skatehousemediacom/6836616032_3d840fe0a2_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p>If you’ve seen the new issue of <a href=\"https://www.skateslate.com/subscriptions-longboarding-magazine/\" target=\"_blank\">SkateSlate magazine</a>, you’ve probably wondered how the hell Louis rolled away from that jersey barrier grind on his downhill board. Rest assured, that shot was a make. Check the full sequence after the grind.<span id=\"more-5128\"></span><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/6836618390/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/how-the-hell-does-louis-do-that-skatehousemediacom/6836618390_f0edc323ac_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p>The technical constraints of off-camera flash photography prevented us from getting a full sequence. Here’s the roll-away.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/6836620694/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/how-the-hell-does-louis-do-that-skatehousemediacom/6836620694_07daccfacb_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/6982754319/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/how-the-hell-does-louis-do-that-skatehousemediacom/6982754319_d826f5da8b_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/6836630062/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/how-the-hell-does-louis-do-that-skatehousemediacom/6836630062_52c4a41272_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/6836634250/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/how-the-hell-does-louis-do-that-skatehousemediacom/6836634250_1d7ab10bb1_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>",
