    "postDate": "2014-06-04",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/l_r36QYg0nE?fs=1&amp;feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The Boomtown Crew started as group of downhill skaters from Eugene, OR  and has now grown to include riders from all over the Pacific Northwest.  We all love to skate, so our number one goal is to spread the stoke and  grow the downhill community by producing videos, organizing events, and  hitting the road to meet and skate with as many people as possible.</p>",
