    "pageTitle": "Comet Skateboards // Presents The Morgan",
    "postDate": "2013-05-25",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NqCEBxRmcPE?rel=0\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>THE MORGAN SIGNATURE MODEL: <a href=\"https://store.cometskateboards.com/morgan\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.cometskateboards.com/morgan</a></p>\n<p>“I designed this board after years of riding the Grease Hammer and Grease Shark. It’s like my final greasy master piece… haha! Anyways, the shape is not much different but slightly improved for greater foot space and function. The new shape paired with improved rocker and concave makes for one of the most comfortable boards I’ve stood on in a while. I’ve felt super locked in and stable during all slides. And let’s be real… the graphic is pretty bangin. Hope you’re feelin it as much as I am!” – Liam Morgan</p>",
