    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/90180050\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/skatesgiving\" target=\"_blank\">Skatesgiving</a> video series is coming to an end. As we get closer towards the conclusion, let’s remember what this annual trip is. It’s a road trip between friends. Getting in a van and skating down mountains is probably the best thing you can do with a grip of your buddies. So get on the road and bomb the closest pass or hike the nearest corner that’s available. Thank you <a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz Skateboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9 Skateboards</a>, Kebbek Skateboards, <a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/home/\" target=\"_blank\">Comet Skateboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.RayneLongboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rayne Longboards</a>, Paris Truck Co, <a href=\"https://radesigns.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RAD Wheels</a>, &amp; Bear Trucks.</p>",
