    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/17143672\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“Hey Guys, I send you this video we made a couple of months ago here in La Plata, Argentina…  Hope You like it! In words of the director: ‘This audiovisual explores longboarding as a sport from the slow motion perspective. Taking time remapping as leitmotiv, we search the way of making contrast between the movement and the tricks of these riders.’</p>\n<p>Riders:  Andres Rubiño, Alejandro Elias, Marcos Contreras, Nico Aon, Nico Dasso, Nico Mac Mahon.” – Nico Mac Mahon</p>",
