    "pageTitle": "Bay Sessions 16: In the Bu",
    "postDate": "2011-12-15",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/77b6h-VTt0M?fs=1&amp;feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Skatehouse had the <em>pleasure</em> of hosting the Bay Sessions crew last week. The crew rolled in deep out of a old beat up civic, tired, greasy, and ready to skate.  We schooled them at beer pong, showed them the hills, and had some gnarly fun runs. Jesse Breiman, you got a little sketch at 1:02. Always stay in your lane, never dive into a blind turn, even if you have to foot break. Way to watch out for the homies though Jesse. Come back soon guys. </p>",
