    "pageTitle": "Grippins 81a, Serves One | SkateHouseMedia.com",
    "postDate": "2013-04-22",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dtSeCGqpgtw\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“GRN TM young gun Spencer Smith, shows what to do when you run out of  wheels. Cook up some more, then go shred them the next day. Well sadly  this isn’t how you actually make wheels but hey it isn’t completely  wrong either! Big thanks goes out to Max Wipperman for film and camera  work. Get stoked, go skate, be safe.”</p>\n<p>Spencer’s Setup: Rayne Nemisis, Aera Trucks 186mm, Abec 11 Grippins 81a</p>",
