    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ey7MIlUq1zw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Sector 9 founders, Steve Lake and Dennis Telfer, are interviewed by Michael  Brooke of ConcreteWave Magazine.&nbsp; Their conversation in tells the origins of  Sector9 and its many achievements in the skateboard  Industry. Through hard work and dedication Steve and Dennis explain how  Sector 9 became what it is today. Crank it up the audio cause it is a bit weak.</p>",
