    "pageTitle": "Getting It in Galena IL | SkateHouseMedia.com",
    "postDate": "2011-04-30",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XfSTe7MVkGM\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“Hey guys i`m huge fan of what you do for the skateboard community and love watching your videos. It really pushes me to become a better skater…. My buddies and I are have an event in Galena IL youve probaly never heard of it haha &nbsp;but its got the gnarlest hill around for us. The main reason im saying this is that we just finished our promo vid and it would make us all stoked!! if you could watch it and maybe give me some feedback. thanks again for all you guys do.” – Mark Eckardt and the Mchenry Co. Riders</p>\n<p>Breaking the 50 mark. If your around the IL area in May be sure to get your board out to support and skate.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=185135981531854\" target=\"_blank\">Click for Race Info</a></p>",
