    "pageTitle": "Rayne Team: Cali Young Gun Steez",
    "postDate": "2013-10-26",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TvCI9gwJpe4?fs=1&amp;feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“The Rayne Team is spread all around the world and each rider brings  their own style and personality into the mix. Come visit SoCal with us  while we hit Laguna Beach California for a NorCal – SoCal meetup between  Rayne Team Riders Jake Fast, Wyatt Gibbs and Levi Green.</p>\n<p>No  matter where you’re from or how wrong your board is, having fun means  skating safe. This video was filmed on legal roads with spotters. Hit up  the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RayneLongboards\" target=\"_blank\">Rayne Facebook Page</a> and find out about legal, safe skating in your  hood.”</p>",
