    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SmOCMSulpsI\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“<a href=\"https://www.raynelongboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rayne Longboards </a>Team Rider Douglas Dalua is a beast, eating up pavement, hills, and wheels like few others in the world. Off the line, no one pushes harder and only a handful are as precise or technically capable of pinning turns and keeping speed like Dalua can. This season Dalua is focused on destroying the the 2011 IGSA Circuito Sudamericano de Downhill (South American Downhill Circuit) and going after the IGSA World Cup title.”</p>",
