    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8632111532/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-byron-essert/8632111532_9a7d5cba14_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></a>Byron came down to visit SoCal on his spring break last week. Max snapped some photos of him on the local hills.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8631003631/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-byron-essert/8631003631_141d5d263b_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"640\"></a>&nbsp; Lil’ B knows that an XL t-shirt shows the speed better. Two more skate shots and a Chance Gaul guest appearance after the jump.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-8499\"></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8631004163/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-byron-essert/8631004163_d02f31f1c8_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></a>Railing left at Roscoe’s Wrecker a couple weeks ago.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8631003301/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-byron-essert/8631003301_0a8f84556f_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></a>Ft. Chance Gaul of Sector 9 fame.</p>",
