    "pageTitle": "Landyachtz: Skate & Explore – Taiwan",
    "postDate": "2011-06-02",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FcZzYmOt-mQ?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz</a> is pleased to bring you their latest tour video, <strong>Skate and Explore: Taiwan</strong>.  Join <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/billy-meiners\">Billy Meiners</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/adam-yates\">Adam Yates</a> and <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/kyle-martin\">Kyle Martin</a> as they experience the people, culture and breathtaking scenery of Taiwan.  The three meet up with local team rider <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/light-liu\">Light Liu</a> and tour around the country skating some of the gnarliest roads Taiwan has to offer.  Fasten your seat belts and brace yourself for a wild ride as we Skate and Explore Taiwan.</p>",
