    "pageTitle": "The “Downhill Disco”  in San Diego on APRIL 30th 2011 | SkateHouseMedia.com",
    "postDate": "2011-05-26",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/R7Jqgx1IfDo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Speed! Slides! Cones! Kickers! Disco Sticks?! You read it right,  folks. There’s gonna be all that and then some. The Downhill Disco will  be held at an undisclosed location in San Diego on APRIL 30th. The hill  in question will be covered in cones, ramps/kickers and possibly a  couple bonus features for your shredding enjoyment.</p>\n<p>There will be a few division for the cones race, as well as a jam-session freeride competition to follow.</p>\n<p>Bring  your longboard, your friends, your cameras, your friends cameras, your  helmets and gloves, and your cheering section to root for your favorite skateboarder.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=149994745061188\" target=\"_blank\">COMPLETE EVENT INFO</a><br>\n<a title=\"https://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=149994745061188\" dir=\"ltr\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=149994745061188\" target=\"_blank\"><br>\n</a></p>",
