    "postDate": "2015-12-26",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/K6QGsBMHgjA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/\">Arbor Skateboards</a> brought five Arbor Downhill team riders to Southern California to showcase the <a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/\">2015 Arbor Downhill Collection</a>. The new collection offers a variety of shapes and each rider was paired with a board that best matched their style of riding with the performance of the board. Find Tyler Howell on the <a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/vugenhausen/\">Vugenhausen</a>, Tom Flinchbaugh on the <a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/highground/\">Highground</a>, Brandon Tissen on the <a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/backlash-40/\">Backlash 40</a>, Jasper Ohlson on the <a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/backlash-37/\">Backlash 37</a> and Ed Garner on the <a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/products/cypher/\">Cypher</a>. </p>",
