    "pageTitle": "Cop Cuts Off Longboarders – Crash",
    "postDate": "2012-12-27",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/CWkpaGbLOa0?rel=0\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Spring is here! Some of our friends were out skating in the B.P.’s in Canada when “A West Vancouver police officer in an unmarked SUV abruptly swerves in front of a group of longboarders to enforce a $35 bylaw violation. Luckily everyone managed to avoid the reckless maneuver. Skate safe!” Before respectful of the communities we skate but remember the <a href=\"https://coastlongboarding.com/\" target=\"_blank\">COAST</a> Slogan: Bombing your Local hills, Outrunning the local Cops!</p>",
