    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/10685022\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe><br>\n“Hello folks, thanks for stopping by to hang with some ‘Coffee &amp;  Judas’. This little flick stars downhill sk8board shredders and my bro’s  Jeff Budro, Erik Lundberg, Louis Pilloni, Evren Ozan &amp; many more.  Your about to catch a glimpse into the randomness throughout the day of  an SDDRL sk8board event, along with the rising talent of Sector 9  riders, below a casual conversation over delicious coffee. This little  flick was made for the Brother’s &amp; Sister’s of downhill sk8board  shredding, and to just all shredders in general. Thankyou everyone for  watching, grab a cup of coffee, sit back &amp; enjoy the show.  I highly  recommend the HD ON experience. Werd.”<br>\n-Kenny Luby</p>",
