    "pageTitle": "If You Can’t Stay Behind, Go Around",
    "postDate": "2013-02-05",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p>Passing cars isn’t something you should do on a regular basis. The driver of this red car saw Matt creeping up behind her, freaked out, and hit the brakes in the middle of the turn. Matt had to go around to avoid smashing into the back of the car. Max lucked out and got the shot. Always skate safely and within your limits!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5636595381/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"car pass 1\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5636595381_7ccbda229e_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5636597901/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"car pass 2\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5636597901_0c19ce2050_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5636604743/in/photostream/\"><img title=\"Car Pass 4\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5636604743_fa1400bd11_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a><br>\nCheck the full size to see the driver’s priceless facial expression in this one.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5636606949/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5636606949_772e18ffe3_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5636609537/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"Car pass\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5636609537_60b7bc99c5_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5636611689/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"carpass\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5636611689_87eed90826_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5636613755/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"passing\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5636613755_9b360b33cd_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5636617381/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"Passed\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5636617381_3eccf0f216_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5637196606/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/if-you-cant-stay-behind-go-around/5637196606_7e93d21581_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\"></a></p>",
