    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/fUi_EfLEHoQ?rel=0\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“HAPPY EASTER!!!!….In celebration of the Easter Holiday, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/scott-lembach\" target=\"_blank\">Scott aka El Beasto</a> invited all the local shredders out for an Easter Egg Hunt Muir style! The team scattered the Easter eggs and all over the whole hill for all the locals skaters to find. Special thanks to our friends at <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9</a> and <a href=\"https://www.radesigns.com/\" target=\"_blank\">RAD</a> for coming out and supporting the scene!” – <a href=\"https://www.muirskate.com\" target=\"_blank\">MuirSkate</a></p>",
