    "pageTitle": "SantaGnarbara: Public Saftey Announcement with Dave Billesbach",
    "postDate": "2014-05-17",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/AGD---Uvxos?rel=0\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Santa Barbara Local, Dave Billesbach, holds it down on his home hill while respecting the rules of the road. If taxpayers are going to continue to build and maintain the roads, the least we can do is respect other road users and residents.</p>\n<p>“This is a public safety announcement with your favorite Santa Gnarabra local, Dave Billesbach. He’ll show you how to do it fast and with style all while keeping it in his own lane. Enjoy! Filmed and Edited by Tom Flinchbaugh”</p>",
