    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/L0ui3E9_i9k?fs=1&amp;feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>As the race season gets officially underway in Australia, skaters get nostalgic for the fun they have on the road with friends. Rayne team riders Graham Buksa, Daniel Hawes and Michael Bowditch love to race, but sometimes it’s the roads between races that make for the most fun with friends. Check them out with some of their bro’s as they rip through Europe wherever they go.</p>\n<p>RIDERS:<br>\nGraham Buksa, Daniel Hawes, Michael Bowditch, and Lachlan Carey</p>\n<p>EDIT:<br>\nDaniel Hawes</p>",
