    "pageTitle": "Brian “Chubbs” Cortright in South Africa",
    "postDate": "2016-04-15",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/126020276\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"Brian Cortright in South Africa\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Donate to Brian’s Recovery:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/sre5dkk\">Brian Go Fund Me</a></p>\n<p>You might know Brian “Chubbs” Cortright as “the Other <a href=\"https://www.calibertruckco.com\">Caliber</a> filmer guy”, he does a ton of great work up in Santa Cruz keeping fresh web content on the net for you. Chubbs rolled with the <a href=\"https://www.calibertruckco.com\">Caliber</a> Crew to film some dank video in South Africa. Once he returned he destroyed his leg at <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/02/05/2015/team-nobull-bayou-battle\">The Bayou Battle Race</a>. Now he has crazy medical bills until he gets recovered. You can help him get back on his feet (literally) by donating to his Go Fund Me.</p>",
