    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/23010655\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“On April 23rd skaters from all over America and Canada converged on the  infamous Maryhill Loops Road for the first day of Deano’s infamous  Spring Freeride.  You can imagine all the sick pack runs that were had  at this event.  But even we had no idea what we were in for.  150+  Riders at once with a helicopter hovering above.  Here’s a taste.    Check skatehousemedia.com for the official event video now in the works!” -<a href=\"https://www.fivemilelongboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Five Mile Longboards</a></p>\n<p>Stay tuned for the helicopter footage on Skate House Media</p>",
