    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lhwFSRYhv1Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“Sat on this footage for a while… But here it is… I pretty much only got the DH race… Took a pretty big hit which is in the video (Also captured by Gardensk8video and featured in this video) … so i kinda sat out a bit…I give a lot of props to the guys who rode that day… I was registered but couldnt bring myself to actually skate it… Pretty intense run and im totally a noob. Glad i could shoot the awesomeness of the day though.” – Jay-Rey Rivera</p>\n<p>The Beast Coast scene is alive and kicking. Even cement curbs wouldn’t slow them down.</p>",
