    "pageTitle": "“They Think They’re Pro Skaters, But They Are Not” | SkateHouseMedia.com",
    "postDate": "2011-12-18",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vxhVzwFnXXQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“Gullwing team riders Danny Tumia and Tyler Martin are like if the Bad News Bears were a skate team. Follow them on there journey down the East Coast where they encounter DIY spots, private bowls, mean girls and  muscle men. Guest appearances by Andrew Mercado, Jeff Budro and Ben Hatchell.”</p>\n<p>Yes this video doesn’t have any downhill but still has plenty of rad skateboarding. Get out and ride your local hills, streets, and parks! Skate Everything just like the guys do over at <a href=\"https://ripcityskate.com/category/media/\" target=\"_blank\">Rip City Skate</a>.</p>",
