    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/41635136?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n</p><p>\nWhen the camera is rolling, it’s easy for riders to push themselves and skate the road to it’s full potential. The plethora of videos filled with unnecessary slides get old quick. Still, remember to skate safe &amp; within your limits. Everything can go wrong in the blink of an eye. </p>",
