    "pageTitle": "Sector 9 | Catalina Classic – Raw Run",
    "postDate": "2016-10-27",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/QLT14lPQMxU?rel=0\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>It’s tighter then it looks and a hell of a lot of fun to skate. Follow the <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/\">Sector 9</a> crew down the track of the Catalina Island Classic. Thanks to <a href=\"https://www.paristruckco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Paris Truck Co.</a> for putting on amazing event.</p>\n<p>“The Downhill Division invaded The Catalina Island Classic winning the race over 128 of the world’s best downhill skateboarders. Follow the Sector 9 team down the race course on this tight technical track as Chance Gaul and Ethan Lau lead the pack. Congratulations to A.J. Haiby on the win!”</p>",
