    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PeHs5ppRHaw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“<a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/matt-kienzle\">Matt Kienzle</a> has been holding it down as a <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/category/scene-supporters/paris-truck-co\">Paris</a> team rider for a solid four years now. In early 2014, we released Matt’s pro truck and since then he’s been putting them through their paces across the world on a variety of challenging terrain. From downhill to freeride, countryside cruising to city shredding, and even on the race circuit – <a href=\"https://www.paristruckco.com\" target=\"_blank\">Paris Trucks</a> can handle it all and look great while doing so. <a href=\"https://shop.resourcedist.com/shop/paris-truck-co-v2-180mm-matt-k-pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Matt K’s pro trucks</a> are no different, we suggest you grab a set today and try ‘em for yourself! (Shoes sold separately.)”</p>",
