    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/23874402\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>If you’ve ever had the pleasure of meeting “Big” Dave Tannaci, even just once, you know you’ll never forget his awesome personality nor his delicious vocabulary.&nbsp; He is always positive, always having fun, and always encouraging everyone else to do the same.&nbsp; Look at the size of that grin, even after getting slapped hard!</p>\n<p>If you’re looking to learn a little more about Big Dave, be sure to check out the <a href=\"https://www.wheelbasemag.com/features/dave-tanacci-interview-recreational-mindgasm/\" target=\"_blank\">interview he recently did with Marcus Bandy over at Wheelbase Magazine</a>.</p>",
