    "pageTitle": "S1 Helmets / Felipe Marin Medellin, Colombia",
    "postDate": "2011-03-18",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/127804030\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"S1 Helmets / Felipe Marin in Medellin Colombia\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"www.s1helmets.com\">S1 Helmets</a> understands that downhill skateboarding is dangerous as hell. To keep pushing the sport it also means higher and higher consequences for crashes. Wearing a hard foam CPSC certified helmet is absolutely essential when skateboarding down hills.<br>\nHere we have a new S1 rider in Medellin, Colombia Felipe Marin who experiences a rather unexpected injury. Remember to always skate safe!</p>",
