    "pageTitle": "Raw Run: Angie’s Curves with Billy Meiners",
    "postDate": "2011-10-07",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/66220291\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz</a> rider, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/billy-meiners\" target=\"_blank\">Billy Meiners</a> takes a run down the next IDF World Cup Race Track, <a href=\"https://angiescurves.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Angie’s Curves</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://angiescurves.com/?p=25\" target=\"_blank\">Rider entries available</a>. Here is the current rider list:<br>\n<iframe style=\"width: 100%; height: 80%; min-height: 500px; border: none;\" src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/pub?key=0Ao3Hm5o8JeQadHNucG5kVUFkel9faEtpLUZkbkZVWEE&amp;gid=2&amp;range=A1:D250\" height=\"300\" width=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>Angie’s Curves – 2013 IDF World Cup – Schedule of Events, Spectator Information, and Volunteer Signup<br>\n</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"more-8783\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Thursday, June 20<sup>th</sup>, 2013</strong></p>\n<p>2:00 pm – Lake Henshaw Resort Campsite Check-in Opens</p>\n<p>5:00 pm – Rider Registration at Lake Henshaw Campground</p>\n<p>7:15 pm – Riders Meeting at Lake Henshaw Campground</p>\n<p>9:30 pm – Casino Night</p>\n<p><strong>Friday, June 21<sup>st</sup> , 2013</strong></p>\n<p>8:00 am – Last Chance Rider Registration at Angie’s Curves Race Track</p>\n<p>9:00 am – Practice Runs All Classes</p>\n<p>12:00 pm – Lunch Break</p>\n<p>1:00 pm – Practice Runs All Classes</p>\n<p>5:00 pm – End of Day 1 Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p>6:00 pm – Pala Skate Park Session</p>\n<p>9:00 pm – Campsite Party</p>\n<p><strong>Saturday, June 22<sup>st</sup>, 2013</strong></p>\n<p>9:00 am – Practice Runs All Classes</p>\n<p>12:00 pm – Lunch Break</p>\n<p>12:30 pm – Qualifying Runs All Classes</p>\n<p>4:00 pm – Practice Runs All Classes if Qualifying is finished</p>\n<p>5:00 pm – End of Day 2 Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p><strong>Sunday, June 23<sup>rd</sup>, 2013</strong></p>\n<p>9:00 am – Practice Runs All Classes</p>\n<p>10:00 am – Junior and Women’s Racing</p>\n<p>12:00 pm – Lunch Break</p>\n<p>12:30 pm – Open Class Practice</p>\n<p>1:45 pm – Open Skateboard Racing</p>\n<p>5:00 pm – End of Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p>7:30 pm – Award Ceremony and Campsite Party at Lake Henshaw Campground</p>\n<p><strong>Spectator Parking and Campground Signup</strong></p>\n<p>-Daily event parking available at the <a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?oe=utf-8&amp;client=firefox-a&amp;ie=UTF-8&amp;q=pala+raceway&amp;fb=1&amp;gl=us&amp;hq=pala+raceway&amp;cid=0,0,7155585424436004713&amp;ei=VmOaUe2DM6GqiALt_oGgAQ&amp;ved=0CKEBEPwSMAA\">Pala Raceway</a> with free shuttle to Angie’s Curves ( No parking available at event venue)</p>\n<p>-Campsite access is $15 dollars for the entirety of the event (4 nights Thurs-Monday) with bathrooms and showers.</p>\n<p>-Email Louis@Sector9.com with camper names (space limited).</p>\n<p><strong>Volunteer at Angie’s Curves Downhill </strong></p>\n<p>- Email Louis@Sector9.com with your contact information and days you can volunteer.</p>\n<p>- Free Camping (Thursday – Monday), Lunch/Dinner provided, Angie’s Shirt and Hat, Sector 9 Gift Package</p>\n<p><strong>Volunteer Schedule</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Tuesday, June 18<sup>th</sup> 2013</strong></p>\n<p>10:00 am – 5:00 pm – Course Setup</p>\n<p><b>Wednesday, June 19<sup>th</sup>, 2013</b></p>\n<p>10:00 am – 5:00 pm – Course Setup</p>\n<p><strong>Thursday, June 20<sup>th</sup>, 2013</strong></p>\n<p>9:00 am – Course Setup</p>\n<p><strong>Friday, June 21<sup>st,</sup> &nbsp;2013</strong></p>\n<p>7:30 am – Volunteer Shuttle Leaves Campground</p>\n<p>8:15 am – Volunteers Meet at Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p>5:45 pm&nbsp;&nbsp; – Volunteer Shuttle Leaves Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p><strong>Saturday, June 22<sup>st</sup>, 2013</strong></p>\n<p>7:30 am – Volunteer Shuttle Leaves Campground</p>\n<p>8:15 am – Volunteers Meet at Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p>5:45 pm&nbsp;&nbsp; – Volunteer Shuttle Leaves Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p><strong>Sunday, June 23<sup>rd</sup>, 2013</strong></p>\n<p>7:30 am – Volunteer Shuttle Leaves Campground</p>\n<p>8:15 am – Volunteers Meet at Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p>5:45 pm&nbsp;&nbsp; – Volunteer Shuttle Leaves Angie’s Curves</p>\n<p><strong>Monday, June 24<sup>th</sup>, 2013</strong></p>\n<p>10:00 am – Course Breakdown</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
