    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/42604412\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/skatesgiving\">Skatesgiving</a> gang selects the lurk option when mother nature destroys the band’s plan.</p>",
