    "pageTitle": "Quick Clips: Jakes Rash 2010 Final Heat",
    "postDate": "2014-10-06",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/12074078\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>It was a wet one at Jakes Rash 2010. Even though there was a constant  downpour creating lake-sized puddles, it didn’t slow the riders down.  Over 40 riders suited up despited the conditions and gave it their all  riding on the edge of traction.</p>\n<p>Congratulations to Housemate James Kelly on Second place.  Who says Californians can’t ride in the rain?</p>\n<p><strong>Results:</strong><br>\n1st Douglas Dalua<br>\n2nd James Kelly<br>\n3rd Kevin Reimer<br>\n4th Zen Shikaze</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/quick-clips-jakes-rash-2010-final-heat/tumblr_l33aspWjI41qaqakr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\"></p>",
