    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IE77Z60-jks?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“It takes a lot of work to create a solid set of skateboard trucks. Probably more than most of us realize. The process from concept to creation can be a long tedious road, but the end result is always worth the work. We’d like to give you a behind the scenes look into our process and introduce you to a few key individuals who make Bear Trucks what it is today. It’s not exactly a science but sometimes you have to treat it as such.”</p>",
