    "postDate": "2012-01-31",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/7304691178/sizes/c/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/francis-cooper-darquea-mauro/7304691178_3cb2a36445_c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"640\"></a></p>\n<p>This little East Coast skate rat has been lurking on our couch for the last few weeks. He says he’s here working on his senior project; but all I’ve seen him do is skate, eat Ritz crackers, and facebook-stalk trashy white girls from East Providence. Squat steez at the rock wall corner on his last run before he went home. Bonus switch check after the jump.<span id=\"more-6062\"></span><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/7304692790/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/francis-cooper-darquea-mauro/7304692790_5d7d66ab8c_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"819\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>",
