    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NdBtc5nKzt4\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://britanniaclassic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">2013 Britannia Classic</a> with the <a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz</a> <a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com/D390.cfm\" target=\"_blank\">Crew</a>.</p>\n<p>Open Results:<br>\n1st <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/Kevin-Reimer\" target=\"_blank\">Kevin Reimer</a><br>\n2nd <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/andrew-chapman\" target=\"_blank\">Andrew Chapman</a><br>\n3rd <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/Adam-Persson\" target=\"_blank\">Adam Persson</a><br>\n4th <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/Matt-Rae\" target=\"_blank\">Matt Rae</a></p>\n<p>Masters Champion: <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/Nico-Desmarais\" target=\"_blank\">Nico Desmarais</a><br>\nLadies Champion: <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/Elena-Corrilgal\" target=\"_blank\">Elena Corrilgal</a><br>\nJuniors Champion: <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/Chance-Gaul\" target=\"_blank\">Chance Gaul</a><br>\nSuper Grom Champion: <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/Quinn-Dubois\" target=\"_blank\">Quinn Dubois</a></p>",
