    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TmgvKhuwkwQ\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>A couple months ago Madrid team riders Max Dubler and Zak Maytum took a trip to the Philippines to check out the scene and do some skating with the rad locals. Riding downhill out there is like a real-life video game–you’re weaving through traffic, dodging livestock, passing cars and wondering what craziness awaits you around the next turn. Check it out.</p>",
