    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/f54gN0bX8f0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Things got wild in the streets of Albuquerque during the Skate School All Around Challenge! A fast hill and urban obstacles made for some aggressive riding. Check out Nick Ronzani’s move at the end.</p>",
    "tags": [],
