    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/5819548452/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" title=\"Pete and Max staying safe\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/max-myers-and-pete-eubank-skatehousemediacom/5819548452_f01783b45e_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"819\"></a>Max Myers and Pete Eubank going fast. Skate, don’t die: stay in your lane on blind corners and never wear headphones when you’re riding downhill.</p>\n<p>Pete rides for <a href=\"https://madridskateboards.com/\">Madrid skateboards</a>. Max rides for <a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/\">Arbor</a> and <a href=\"https://ripcityskate.com/\">Rip City Skate</a>.</p>",
