    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://landyachtz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz Longboards</a> rider <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/tags/steven-vera\" target=\"_blank\">Steven Vera</a> was killing it all weekend at <a href=\"https://skatesunpeaks.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Skate Sun Peaks</a>. Our old housemate <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/tags/matt-kienzle\" target=\"_blank\">Matt K</a> got ambitious and went for the run through with this real <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/category/raw-run\" target=\"_blank\">raw run</a>.</p>",
