    "pageTitle": "Event Coverage: Switchbacks",
    "postDate": "2014-08-01",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/131465763\" width=\"700\" height=\"420\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Portland, Oregon has it good. Skateboarding is completely legal throughout the city and there’s even a train to bring you to the <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/?s=zoobomb\">top</a>. The guys at <a href=\"https://pdxdownhill.com\">PDX Downhill</a> puts together a fine race series for the up &amp; coming scene.</p>\n<p>1st – Brandon Tissen (<a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/\" target=\"_blank\">Arbor</a>, <a href=\"https://calibertruckco.com\" target=\"_blank\">Caliber</a>, <a href=\"https://skatebloodorange.com\" target=\"_blank\">Blood Orange</a>).<br>\n2nd – Conner Stanek.<br>\n3rd – Devon Dotson.<br>\n4th – Casey Morrow (<a href=\"https://arborcollective.com/skateboards/\" target=\"_blank\">Arbor</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.gullwingtruckco.com\" target=\"_blank\">Gullwing</a>).</p>",
