    "pageTitle": "Photos: James Kelly",
    "postDate": "2015-11-06",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9155117701/sizes/c/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-james-kelly/9155117701_ab361e58bb_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></a></p>\n<p>Last week we put out a video of Max Dubler shooting some photos of James (Arbor, Caliber, RAD, Venom) in a rarely-skated California canyon. These are the photos they got that day. As always, click through for full resolution.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-james-kelly/9157356630_3aa7b3973c_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></p>\n<p>This shot ran as a double-page spread in the last issue of <a href=\"https://www.skateslate.com/category/longboarding-magazine-2/\" target=\"_blank\">SkateSlate magazine</a>. Four more bangers after the jump.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-9144\"></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9157373820/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-james-kelly/9157373820_b212c1dea6_b.jpg\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9157368722/sizes/c/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-james-kelly/9157368722_74fe03e49b_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9157366010/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-james-kelly/9157366010_77bbacbe1c_b.jpg\" width=\"819\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9155105591/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-james-kelly/9155105591_e00f3118df_b.jpg\" width=\"683\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>",
