    "postDate": "2013-05-05",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/45106350\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The 2012 Maryhill Festival of Speed is concluded. <a href=\"https://www.raynelongboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rayne</a>‘s <a href=\"www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/patrick-switzer\" target=\"_blank\">Patrick Switzer</a> took home the bacon.<br>\nA number of other incidents occurred. <a href=\"www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/zak-maytum\" target=\"_blank\">Zak Maytum</a> broke the track record &amp; an absurd deathmatch mini ramp contest thanks to <a href=\"https://www.gullwingtruckco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Gullwing</a>, <a href=\"https://www.ripcityskate.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rip City</a>, &amp; <a href=\"https://sector9.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9</a>. Race heat quandaries made for a lot disqualifications &amp; <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/jon-huey\" target=\"_blank\">Jon Huey</a> took butt boarding hands down. <a href=\"https://oslphoto.tumblr.com/\">OSL</a> Thumbnail.</p>",
