    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/132487124\" width=\"700\" height=\"393\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n</p><p><a href=\"https://vimeo.com/132487124\">S1 Helmets / Colombian Water Boys</a> from <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/s1helmetco\">s-one helmet co / s1helmets</a> on <a href=\"https://vimeo.com\">Vimeo</a>.</p>\n<p>In Bogota, Colombia it rains in the mountains nearly every single day. Wet and patchy downhill bombs are the local’s specialty. Check <a href=\"https://s1helmets.com\">S1 Helmets</a> team riders Chela, Juanito, Yepes, David, and Mateo hitting a 10/10 chunder bomb and a few ridge runs that lead to the city.</p>",
