    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/13075930\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>2010 Voss Downhill Championship Results:</strong><br>\n1. Jackson Shapiera<br>\n2. Christoffer Sanne<br>\n3. Alex Horthe<br>\n4. Torbjorn Sunde<br>\n5. Louis Pilloni<br>\n6. Robin Sandberg</p>\n<p>While these guys are in Norway, the <a href=\"https://www.igsaworldcup.com/\" target=\"_blank\">IGSA World Cup at Maryhill</a> is going on. Check out some of the action from the rest of the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9_zOJ_iysL8\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9 crew</a>.</p>",
