    "pageTitle": "Raw Run Whistler: Sector 9 Team",
    "postDate": "2015-12-05",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/99962508?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;color=9e0000\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>After two days of the riding at the Whistler World Cup the race brackets are set (<a href=\"https://www.internationaldownhillfederation.org/profiles/blogs/jimmy-riha-qualifies-1st-at-whistler\" target=\"_blank\">Qualifying Results</a>).&nbsp; During one of the practice runs, Louis grabbed the polecam for a run with the <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9</a> crew down the race course.</p>\n<p><strong>Open Skateboard Times</strong><br>\n1 Jimmy Riha 00:01:47.77<br>\n2 Patrick Switzer 00:01:48.07<br>\n3 Key Dougherty 00:01:48.09<br>\n4 Louis Pilloni 00:01:48.09<br>\n5 Alex Tongue 00:01:48.27<br>\n6 Jackson Shapiera 00:01:48.31<br>\n7 Zak Maytum 00:01:48.34<br>\n8 Connor Ferguson 00:01:48.51<br>\n9 Riley Harris 00:01:48.60<br>\n10 Dillon Stephens 00:01:48.72<br>\n11 Micah Green 00:01:48.86<br>\n12 Kevin Reimer 00:01:48.92<br>\n13 Calvin Staub 00:01:49.09<br>\n14 Brendan Davidson 00:01:49.28<br>\n15 Nick Breton 00:01:49.31<br>\n16 James Kelly 00:01:49.33<br>\n17 Byron Essert 00:01:49.65<br>\n18 Bryce Brady 00:01:49.78<br>\n19 Michael Fitter 00:01:49.87<br>\n20 Josh Rolf 00:01:49.88</p>",
