    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/99896340\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The second race of the 2014 IDF World Cup Series is currently underway in Whistler, British Colombia. With 7 hairpins, rough pavement, and 6 man heats racing will be getting tight and intense. 2013 IDF world cup 5th place finisher <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/dillon-stephens\" target=\"_blank\">Dillon Stephens</a> shows us the tight lines of the track as Louis Pilloni follows him down. They both go a little wide in the first hairpin but lay down a solid run after that. Dillon rides for <a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz Skateboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.beartrucks.com/index.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">Bear Trucks</a> and <a href=\"https://hawgswheels.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Hawgz wheels</a>.</p>",
