    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/aoi7G5RX6sk?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“Longboard Girls Crew proudly presents the journey of five girls to the first Maryhill She-ride. Ishtar, Pam, Amanda, Marisa &amp; Daisy will rock every road, from LA to Maryhill, and will immortalize an epic trip to the first female-only free ride in one of the most DH epic spots. We’re stoked.</p>\n<p>Special thanks to Daddies Board Shop, <a href=\"https://www.abec11.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Abec 11</a>, Skatera Skate Wear, Blue Sky Longboard, <a href=\"https://www.raynelongboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Rayne Longboards</a>, <a href=\"https://www.Sector9.com\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9</a>, Encargo PAQ, Riptide Bushings, Kahalani, <a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/home/\" target=\"_blank\">Comet</a>, Orangatang. Stay tunned!”</p>",
