    "pageTitle": "Cowtown",
    "postDate": "2013-01-10",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/26653405\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Rumors and maps of a new road up in NorCal had piqued our interest; but we hadn’t gotten around to actually skating it until March, when Blake Smith invited Pete Eubank and Max to come make a video with Sinjin Davis. The road didn’t disappoint, and after way more “warm-up” runs than we really needed, we got down to business and filmed this.</p>\n<p>Blake definitely knows how to use a camera, and his website <a href=\"https://www.northstatedownhill.com/\" target=\"_blank\">North State Downhill</a> is stacked with sick videos and quality photos of NorCal’s many shredders. Check it out.</p>\n<p>Crucial thanks to Madrid and Venom.</p>",
