    "pageTitle": "Event Coverage: IGSA Maryhill 2011",
    "postDate": "2011-11-17",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/26724676\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Curious to know what happen during this year’s IGSA Maryhill? Click and enjoy. Special thanks to <a href=\"https://www.yvonvite.ch/\" target=\"_blank\">Yvonvite Labarthe</a> for the video.</p>\n<p><strong>Results:</strong><br>\n1. Ramon Konigshausen, Switzerland<br>\n2. Tim Del Rosario-Rojas, United States<br>\n3. Billy Meiners, United States<br>\n4. Graham Buksa, Canada<br>\n5. Zen Shikazi, Canada<br>\n6. Martin Siegrist, Switzerland<br>\n7. Joshua Torres, United States<br>\n8. Mike Snyder, United States<br>\n9. Max Wippermann, United States<br>\n10. Tommy Waton, United States<br>\n11. Andrew Chapman, Canada<br>\n12. Brian Cortright, United States</p>",
