    "pageTitle": "Locals: Norwegian Groms",
    "postDate": "July 21, 2015",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p>During the week of <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/?s=Ekstremsportveko\">Ekstremsportveko</a>, riders are encouraged to contribute footage towards a daily video. <a href=\"https://www.paristruckco.com\">Paris Truck Co</a>‘s Ali Nas crushed the game all week. Saturday’s video of the event features these Norwegian groms: Johannes Aalhom, Magne Ørvik, Jørund Bratset, and Jens S. Øvregård. While the group cruises down a run called “Donald” in Norway, take note of&nbsp;Johannes Aalhom’s stance. You might recognize Johannes from this <a href=\"https://www.rumbleattheranch.com\">Rumble At The Ranch</a> heat where he races <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/01/05/2015/rumble-at-the-ranch-round-1-heats-13-16\">Max Ballesteros</a>.</p>",
