    "postDate": "2012-06-08",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/25698308\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“Hey SkateHouse – Just wanted to say thanks for posting the <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/04/28/2011/dear-louie\" target=\"_blank\">Pro Callout video</a> a while back. We loved reading all of the hateful youtube comments we received! Figured I’d send you guys over a couple of new videos we cranked out as our local game of GNAR continues. One of them is a quick preview for the full length gnar movie that we’re releasing after this season, and one is just a random little edit. Anyways hope you guys make it to Montana to skate someday. We’ve got some sick hills and very low traffic, just got to watch out for bears, moose, dear, snowbanks and other gnarly shit instead. See you soon.”</p>\n<p>-Noah and the rest of <a href=\"https://www.406downhill.com\" target=\"_blank\">406 Downhill</a></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/26697463\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>",
