    "pageTitle": "Raw Run: IDF Kozokov Challenge 2013",
    "postDate": "2013-11-23",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/71237070?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;color=9e0000\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>With over 170 downhill skateboarders at the <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/10/31/2012/shm-euro-trip-part-1-kozakov\" target=\"_blank\">Kozokov Challenge</a>, racing gets tighter and tighter each year. Take a run down the track with the 2nd through 5th place finishers as Louis follows the crew with <a href=\"https://madridskateboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Team Madrid’s</a> Abarth 500.</p>\n<p><strong>Results:</strong><br>\n1st – Zak Maytum<br>\n2nd – Adam Persson<br>\n3rd – Patrick Switzer<br>\n4th – James Kelly<br>\n5th – Dillon Stephens<br>\n6th – Calvin Staub<br>\n7th – Louis Pilloni<br>\n8th – Kyle Martin</p>",
