    "postDate": "2015-12-04",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/fJvYHA8wsAw?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The South East Grom Squad plus a californian took a trip to the NC Mountains. Shout out to all the people who are a part of local bombit for making all of this happen. Grab some friends, hop in a car, and go skate!</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/_qpDN-ZGO7E?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“Yooo skate house whats good! Southeast grom squad hit some shit this past week on a little tour we had. spent some time in hashville and boone. we got stacked footy. thought I’d share some of our stuff with you, spread that stoke and shtuff. Lil raw run i got down secret surf spot filmed by the homie philip skaar! keep it gucci” – Garrett Gourley</p>",
