    "pageTitle": "Raw Run: Graveyard Call",
    "postDate": "2016-07-22",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/13891797\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Follow along as Housemate Louis Pilloni films a run down the race  course with buddies Kevin Reimer, Patrick Switzer and Scoot Smith at the  IGSA World Cup: Graveyard Call in France. For an event recap check out  the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.igsaworldcup.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=463&amp;Itemid=465\" target=\"_blank\">IGSA</a> homepage.</p>\n<p><strong>Results:</strong><br>\n1. Kevin Reimer, Canada<br>\n2. Patrick Switzer, Canada<br>\n3. Louis Pilloni, United States<br>\n4. Evren Ozan, United States<br>\n5. Stefan Rufli, Switzerland<br>\n6. James Kelly, United States<br>\n7. Ramon Konigshausen, Switzerland<br>\n8. Phillipe Dupuy, France<br>\n9. Christoph Batt, Switzerland<br>\n10. Adam Persson, Sweden</p>",
