    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/71589349\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>17 Hairpins, 5 days, and endless shuttles up the hill gives you all the skateboarding you could ask for at the the <a href=\"https://knk.longboard.si/\" target=\"_blank\">KnK Bear’s Guts Freeride</a>. Follow a run down with <a href=\"https://skatebloodorange.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Blood Orange</a> and <a href=\"https://www.muirskate.com\" target=\"_blank\">Muir Skate</a> rider, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/byron-essert\" target=\"_blank\">Byron Essert</a>, as he navigates his way down the run.</p>",
