    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/135432718\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" title=\"Raw Run: COASH - Chill on a Swiss Hill\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The best part of traveling to downhill events is skating all the surrounding terrain. Max Ballesteros (<a href=\"https://www.muirskate.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Muir</a>, <a href=\"https://www.radesigns.com/\" target=\"_blank\">R.A.D.</a>) takes some runs with soon to be Swiss citizen, Patrick Switzer, down a classic. Patrick has been skating these hills since his first <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gzyAN5sXao8\" target=\"_blank\">Euro Tour in 2009</a>.</p>",
