    "pageTitle": "Almabtrieb 2010 World Championships – S9 Edition",
    "postDate": "2012-09-18",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q_YtFPI_BoM?fs=1&amp;feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Louis, James, and friends were up in the action at this years World Championships.</p>\n<p><strong>Results:<br>\n1</strong> Reimer Kevin CAN<br>\n<strong>2 </strong>Shapiera Jackson AUS<strong><br>\n3 </strong>Switzer Patrick CAN<br>\n<strong>4 </strong>Lundberg Erik SWE <strong><br>\n5 </strong>Batt Cristoph SUI<br>\n<strong>6 </strong>Smith Scoot CAN<br>\n<strong>7 </strong>Silva Douglas (Dalua) BRA<br>\n<strong>8 </strong>Kelly James USA<br>\n<strong>9</strong> Königshausen Ramon SUI<br>\n<strong>10</strong> Robert Nicolas SUI<br>\n<strong>11</strong> Dietz Alex GER<br>\n<strong>12</strong> Nas Ali NOR<br>\n<strong>13</strong> Pilloni Louis USA<br>\n<strong>14 </strong>Erban Mischo CAN<br>\n<strong>15</strong> Lessa Thiago Gomes BRA<br>\n<strong>16</strong> Smith Spencer USA</p>",
