    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/102875439\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/eric-jensen\">Eric Jensen</a> just recently got his license so he packed all his stuff in his car to explore different skate spots across America on a two month tour. Of course he found his way to the west coast to hit up some California golden runs. With his <a href=\"https://store.cometskateboards.com/farmer/\" target=\"_blank\">Comet Farmer</a> and <a href=\"https://calibertruckco.com/team/eric-jensen/\" target=\"_blank\">Caliber Trucks</a> under his feet we was gonna keep on rolling even if car ran out of gas. Bad Decisions Alex meet up with Jensen to capture the action.</p>",
