    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/71723354?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;color=9e0000\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Two years after Endless Roads, <a href=\"https://longboardgirlscrew.com\" target=\"_blank\">Longboard Girls Crew</a> hits the road again. This new trip takes 14 female riders from different places and cultures to experience through skating one of the oldest places on earth: Israel. The riders are Amanda Powell, Katie Nielson, Marisa Nuñez, Cindy Zhou, Cami Best, Gina Mendez, Jenna Ruso, Ishtar Bäcklund, Eider Walls, Cristina Mandarina, Micaela Wilson, Gador Salis, Jacky Madenfrost &amp; Valeria Kechichian. Help them out through <a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/open-lgc-skates-israel\" target=\"_blank\">indiegogo</a>.</p>",
