    "pageTitle": "Photos: Angie’s Curves",
    "postDate": "2016-10-21",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9575420045/sizes/c/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-angies-curves/9575420045_d542670199_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\"><br>\n</a>Angie’s Curve itself is crazy steep. <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/louis-pilloni\">Louis</a> had it under control, though.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/angies-curves\">Angie’s</a> was the gnarliest race ever. Max took some photos. More after the jump.</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-9655\"></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9575426001/sizes/c/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-angies-curves/9575426001_16f0f73771_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\"></a>Swiss and extrordinarily stable on those Magun trucks,&nbsp;Jolanda Vogler footbrakes through the wreckage in the approach to Angie’s Curve.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9578208618/sizes/h/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-angies-curves/9578208618_0e047a594f_h.jpg\" width=\"1067\" height=\"1600\"></a>Turn 7 was where the realness of reality was in full effect. <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/james-kelly\">James</a> was one of a few dudes that went full balls every run, tucking in to a toeside at a real-life 60+ miles an hour, which is like 74 on the internet.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9575422579/sizes/k/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-angies-curves/9575422579_f5a20196e5_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></a>This is a chick breaking her ankle after she wobbled out and tumbled in the fast chicane. Your foot isn’t supposed to bend that way.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9578211280/sizes/c/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-angies-curves/9578211280_dc02d6369c_c.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"><br>\n</a>Most people can’t rock a clear visor without looking dumb. <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/spencer-smith\">Spencer Smith</a> can.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/9578217334/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-angies-curves/9578217334_6a2ce2f82f_b.jpg\" width=\"819\" height=\"1024\"></a>Local boy <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/duke-degen\">Duke Degen</a> went hard in his quiet way, making second in the final.</p>",
    "tags": [],
    "categories": [
      "Event Coverage",
      "Photos"
    ],
