    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/72912221?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;color=9e0000\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://calibertruckco.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Caliber</a> gang headed up to Summerland, British Columbia for what is arguably the best event in downhill skateboarding – the <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/giants-head-freeride\" target=\"_blank\">Giant’s Head Freeride</a>. The combination of an epic road, skater-built features, 250 skaters, and an amazing crew of organizers culminated in the GHF crew’s best event to date. Enjoy these captured moments of <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/eric-jensen\" target=\"_blank\">Eric Jensen</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/alicia-fillback\" target=\"_blank\">Alicia Fillback</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/ethan-cochard\" target=\"_blank\">Ethan Cochard</a> destroying everything in their path.</p>",
