    "pageTitle": "2010 Cathlamet Champion: James Kelly",
    "postDate": "2015-04-28",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/14611285\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Congratulations to housemate James Kelly for winning the 2010&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cathlametcorral.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Cathlamet Downhill Corral</a>. After placing second at <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=90WvYphYjtM\" target=\"_blank\">last years race</a>,  he came back strong battling through a field of 85 riders and two  kicker ramps to earn a victory. Stay tuned for the full event recap  video.</p>\n<p><strong>Results:</strong><br>\n1. James Kelly<br>\n2. Alex Tongue<br>\n3. Casey Morrow<br>\n4. Robin McGuirk<br>\n5. Zak Maytum<br>\n6. Dennis Manougian<br>\n7. Nick Calafato<br>\n8. Billy Meiners</p>",
