    "pageTitle": "Comet Skateboards // Brucin’ USA Trailer",
    "postDate": "2015-11-10",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/PJBJJCRh4p4?rel=0\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Comet Skateboards</a> sent Eric Jensen and friends across the great states of the USA with Matt Bo tagging along to document it all. From skateparks to ditches to mountain passes, Brucin USA shows the <a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/team\" target=\"_blank\">Comet team</a> shredding all types of terrain with all types of styles. Get inspired, grab some friends and a vehicle then hit the road.</p>\n<p>Featuring Eric Jensen, Anthony Flis, Jared Henry, Nick Ketner, Nick Ronzani, Brian Peck, Big Dave, and a whole host of other familiar faces.</p>\n<p>Comet will be hosting premiers at skate shops over the next few weeks. If your interested in having one in your local area please email team@cometskateboards.com and tell your local shop!</p>",
