    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/73826094?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=9e0000\" height=\"394\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“<a href=\"https://www.arborcollective.com\" target=\"_blank\">Arbor Skateboards</a> is proud to announce our newest team rider – <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/?s=Tyler+Howell\" target=\"_blank\">Tyler Howell</a>! A Santa Barbara local, Tyler Howell takes a naturally fluid California style of downhill skating and matches it with his powerful and technical determination. His approach is unique and gives a new look for skaters to aspire to. In his <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ZT3YsWuJUc\" target=\"_blank\">first video</a> with Arbor (film/edit Jack Boston), Tyler demonstrates what it means to skate hard and fast on the Santa Barbara Mountains. He is riding the <a href=\"https://www.arborcollective.com/skate/boards/view/426741/vgenhausen\" target=\"_blank\">2013 Vugenhausen</a> as his preferred board for these mountain roads. Now enjoy as you see the chill vibes of Santa Barabara get paired with Johnny Cash and some downhill skateboarding.”</p>",
