    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/74480953?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;color=9e0000\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>We had the opportunity to skate some pretty epic mountain passes on the 2013 <a href=\"https://www.madridskateboards.com\" target=\"_blank\">Madrid</a> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IWCc2QtxlK8&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\">Europe Tour</a>. The locals told us to hit the Swiss roads early in the morning because there’s crazy traffic, but that didn’t happen so we had to hit each road once and move on. This footage is Zak’s first and only run down this hill, and he went all out. Enjoy.</p>",
