    "pageTitle": "Fall Freeride, Extra Rowdy",
    "postDate": "2012-04-30",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/9ybFYpVCnOA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>As everyone gets better at skating, the pack riding at Maryhill Freerides keeps getting crazier. It was unbelievably hot this time around; so lots of people decided to take their chances and hit the hill raw dog–a brave move when Coop’s around.</p>\n<p>While everyone kept it together most of the time, quite a few people went home with some road rash. Fortunately, their bad luck was caught on film and is presented here for your entertainment.</p>\n<p>Special thanks to Lee Cation, Jaden Chavez, Frank Cote, Jacob Gellatly, and Zak Maytum for the footage.</p>",
