    "pageTitle": "Soldiers of Downhill October 15-16 – Sign Up Now",
    "postDate": "2011-04-16",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SOD2011-1.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3551\" title=\"SOD2011-1\" src=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/SOD2011-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\" height=\"664\"></a></p>\n<p>October 15-16, 2011, 9am Saturday to 6pm Sunday come ride the infamous, “Jester Hill,” in beautiful Bainbridge&nbsp; Ohio, during The Fall Festival of the Leaves. Eat a fried&nbsp; snickers bar, sleep in an abandon school, party with the locals, and go&nbsp; really fast down a fun hill!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ohiodownhillskate.com/register/\" target=\"_blank\">Register Now!</a></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/89ev1M1NbuA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Two days of luge and skate!</p>\n<p>Day One:&nbsp; practice runs all day<br>\nDay two:&nbsp; practice runs/race</p>\n<p>Camping Friday night and Saturday night at the bottom of the hill is free with registration.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/16145489\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/event.php?eid=115427065212833\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook Event Page</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.silverfishlongboarding.com/forum/events-races-skates-series/189440-soldiers-downhill-2011-a-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><br>\nSilverfish Discussion Page</a></p>",
