    "pageTitle": "Blood Orange Product Highlight: Griptape",
    "postDate": "2012-03-13",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/JOBVTiQNrW4?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Take a moment to enjoy an outing with Aaron From the Block as he skates us through his favorite features of the new <a href=\"https://skatebloodorange.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Blood Orange</a> Griptape.<br>\nNew features:<br>\n* Increased grit size for added control<br>\n* Refined, ultra-sharp grit for superior traction<br>\n* Specially-coated surface for long-lasting durability<br>\n* Extra-tacky, thin backing allows for edge wrapping, if that’s your game<br>\n* Non-Toxic and Earth Friendly…Hooray!<br>\n* Tons of juicy colors to choose from<br>\n*4 sheets per pack for a total coverage of 40″ x 11″<br>\nAlong with our riders input, we developed a heavy-duty super-coarse grit for maximum traction. Tacky, but not overly grippy, you will love Blood Orange griptape under your feet whether you’re freeriding or racing.</p>",
