    "pageTitle": "Photos: Kozakov Challenge",
    "postDate": "2016-02-25",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8016364536/sizes/h/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-kozakov-challenge/8016364536_31dd14a1a5_c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></a></p>\n<p>Team Skatehouse gettin’ in it on the first righty. Big Lou doesthe light dude grippy wheels carve ‘n’ grip while James and Matt get their toeside predrifit on.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8016364908/sizes/h/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-kozakov-challenge/8016364908_8fc6ebb2a7_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"819\" height=\"1024\"></a></p>\n<p>Stefan Risch has the most excellent all-gold set of NJKs. Check the tip ‘n’ rip.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8016361617/sizes/h/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-kozakov-challenge/8016361617_88c92c803a_c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\"></a></p>\n<p>Sebastian Hertler follows Dalua through the second righty while Luke Melo brings up the rear. Check the rubber lip on his aerolid.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8016364162/sizes/h/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-kozakov-challenge/8016364162_cd8a70f76a_c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"640\"></a></p>\n<p>Louie holding on in the fast righty.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8016363382/sizes/h/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-kozakov-challenge/8016363382_edd6fd1040_c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\"></a></p>\n<p>Chip Wood and Braden Tibbles in the fast righty.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/8016362333/sizes/o/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/photos-kozakov-challenge/8016362333_f335b3391c_o.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"565\" height=\"706\"></a></p>\n<p>Unknown lil’ homie with the euro-spec smoking footbrake.</p>",
