    "pageTitle": "A Secret History of the Ollie",
    "postDate": "2012-03-14",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/craigsnyder/pop-culture-odyssey-a-secret-history-of-the-ollie/widget/video.html\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"> </iframe></p>\n<p>Our good friend Jonathan Harms has spent countless hours working with author Craig Snyder to put out a book titled <em>A Secret History of the Ollie</em>.  To quote JBH, “The book mixes Craig’s own documentation with dozens of interviews and other primary sources. It focuses on the creation and advancement of the ollie, but in doing so it also does an admirable job of documenting the history of skateboarding itself.”  </p>\n<p>Now the guys need our help to fund the printing of the book, so if you have a few minutes and value beautiful and accurate documentation of skateboarding’s rich history, check out their project and consider donating a few bucks.  Thanks!  <a href=\"https://kck.st/1Cj3hgQ\">https://kck.st/1Cj3hgQ</a></p>",
