    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/vd-pxRFO_ko?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>From the mind of Turnco’s Skip Marcotte, the Subsonic Sidewalk Showdown was a skateboard race course like no other and a favorite among many. Riders had to negotiate erratic slalom cone setups that took them onto bank walls, sidewalks, pump lumps, and steep difficult ramps.</p>\n<p>Podium:<br>\nBrandon Tissen, Will Royce, Casey Morrow</p>",
