    "postDate": "2016-10-27",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/IGU9dDFtT9Q?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“As the <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9 </a>Downhill Division traveled country to country attending various skateboard events and <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/?s=idf\" target=\"_blank\">IDF World Cup</a> Races, the best skate destinations were often found traveling to the next event. Follow Sector 9 Team Rider, <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/team.php?team=downhill&amp;member_id=172\" target=\"_blank\">Brendan Davidson</a>, as he takes his first run down this glorious alp road. This follow run shows less then half of the full run as the full run finishes deep in the forest. Always <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/category/learning-curve\" target=\"_blank\">skate withing your abilities</a>, <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ut0wObzLCeI\" target=\"_blank\">wear the proper safety equipment</a>, and have fun.”</p>",
