    "pageTitle": "The Sullivan Challenge | SkateHouseMedia.com",
    "postDate": "2012-04-05",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/30083800\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>A grip of the SHM crew was able to make it to the Sullivan Challenge in Kimberly BC. The race is know for its unique set of rules and crazy odd track. Its always crazy when Jodi is in charge…</p>\n<p>Sullivan Results:<br>\n1st Zen Shikaze<br>\n2nd Billly Meiners<br>\n3rd Zak Maytum<br>\n4th Nick Breton<br>\n5th Casey Morrow<br>\n6th Hugh Johnston<br>\n7th Jeff Woodfine<br>\n8th Louis Pilloni</p>",
