    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/hNkA5aUOlfo?rel=0\" height=\"525\" width=\"700\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The Rayne Team knows how to do it. Go to events, skate, and have a good time. That is how it is done. If skateboarding isn’t fun, why are you doing it?</p>\n<p>“For years we have been going to events and making fun edits about the course, the event and the travel to and from, this year we decided to take one of our favorite events and give you a little behind the scenes taste of what it means to spend 4 days around a hill in small town with 200+ friends… skate every day? Party every night!” – <a href=\"https://www.RayneLongboards.com\" target=\"_blank\">Rayne Longboards</a></p>",
