    "pageTitle": "Event Coverage: Menlo Park Slide Jam 2012",
    "postDate": "2013-02-21",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/51301841\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Menlo Park 2012 was a blast. In its third year running the contest went off flawlessly. Menlo features 2 days of freeriding on a closed hill, a Friday night skate park jam, and a camp site to host all the skaters complete with music, food, and drink. Skaters from up and down the west coast came out to shred some thane and have a good time. Huge thanks to David Hiltbrand and the Sunset Sliders form making it happen year after year.</p>\n<p>Big thanks to <a href=\"https://www.muirskate.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Muir Skate </a>for providing us to the event.</p>",
    "tags": [],
    "categories": [
      "Event Coverage"
    ],
    "contentUrls": [
      "https://www.muirskate.com",
      "https://player.vimeo.com/video/51301841"
    ],
    "ranking": 2,
