    "pageTitle": "Soldiers of Downhill Finals | SkateHouseMedia.com",
    "postDate": "2014-09-04",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/30779247\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n</p><p>The race and freeride ran smoothly allowing riders to get more runs in on both days than last year.  Overall the event was a great success and everyone seemed to leave happy.  We also double the number of riders for stand-up from last year and had about the same for luge and classic.  There is already a <a href=\"https://teamquebec.org/2011/10/18/soldiers-of-downhill-2011/\" target=\"_blank\">write-up and pictures</a> from the event. The final results for stand-up:</p>\n<p>1. Nicolas Desmarais (Niko)<br>\n2. AJ Haiby<br>\n3. Mike Jakubiec (Jakoop)<br>\n4. William Royce<br>\n5. Cam Brickenden<br>\n6. Pascal Jean (Rookie)<br>\n7. Dan Oliver<br>\n8. Jeremy Ross</p>\n<p>-Sean Graves”</p>",
