    "pageTitle": "Kevin Kang: Raw Run: Vol 1",
    "postDate": "2013-02-22",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//player.vimeo.com/video/101478532?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;color=9e0000\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Kevin Kang straight up killing it a technical road. It’s always steeper then it looks. </p>\n<p>“Hey Skatehouse! Huge fan and supporter of the scene here. My name is Thomas Richmond and I am from Asheville, NC and skate with the AGP Crew on the East Coast crushing all the mountain roads. I currently ride for Comet skateboards and do a lot of video editing for them as well. Myself and the AGP crew just released a Raw Run of our friend Kevin Kang ABSOLUTELY crushing a secret hill on the East Coast. I would love for you guys to check this video out and hopefully post it up on the skatehouse media site. we have a Vimeo plus account for high quality videos and it will look nice when embedded. We also film with a full frame Canon 6D and a Rokinon 14mm. I did the camera/edit and Matt Deitch did the follow car run. Check the edit here, it already has over 4k views in a few days!” </p>\n<p>Driver: Matt Deitch<br>\nCamera/Edit: Thomas Richmond<br>\nSong: “Left Hand Free” by: Alt-J</p>",
