    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WjnWdCxmiXE\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>In the first installment of the 2011 Get Elevated Series, the team meets up at the Skate House in Los Angeles before heading NE into the mountains. After a long drive and by sheer serendipity, they find a driving guide which leads road nestled in the mountain range nearby. Turns out the pavement is super burly and features huge cracks across the road the entire way down. After the impromptu session is over, the team rests their heads in Mammoth Lakes in preparation to skate the area the following day. Days 2 and 3 featured in the next episode.</p>",
