    "bodyText": "<p>Spain Squad Jorge Pernes, Toti Motocicleta (<a href=\"https://beartrucks.com/\">Bear</a>), and Oriol Calico (<a href=\"https://www.rdvxgriptape.com/\">RDVX</a>,<a href=\"https://originalskateboards.com/\">Original</a>) took a trip to a volcanic island to visit Marcos Costa for some skating. There the boys found endless hairpins and a thick morning marine layer rolling in over the hills.</p>",
