    "pageTitle": "Road Trip: Dominican Republic",
    "postDate": "2014-04-22",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/52367594\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/pam-diaz\" target=\"_blank\">Pam Diaz</a> persuaded housemate <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/matthew-kienzle\" target=\"_blank\">Matt K</a> to visit the Dominican Republic for the Jacagua Extreme Downhill race. She also got <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/amanda-powell\" target=\"_blank\">Amanda Powell</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/jose-guzman\" target=\"_blank\">Jose Guzman</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/byron-essert\" target=\"_blank\">Byron Essert</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/molly-lewis\" target=\"_blank\">Molly Lewis</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/scott-lembach\" target=\"_blank\">Scott Lembach</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/evren-ozan\" target=\"_blank\">Evren Ozan</a>, &amp; <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/liam-morgan\" target=\"_blank\">Liam Morgan</a> to come on the quick trip to the DR. Pam Diaz packed up all the visitors into a van and showed us the steepest action the Dominican had to offer.</p>",
