    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/16640999\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Our good friend Hugh “Kibbling” Johnston recently stopped by for another  stay and brought along with him “Prince” Dillon Stephens, another  shredder from British Columbia.  They figured LA was a logical stop  along the way from Canada to Peru and Brazil, and they’ve been shredding  hills everywhere they go.  Thanks for coming by, boyees!</p>",
