    "pageTitle": "R.A.D. Crew Adventures: California Coastal Mountains – Part 1 Malibu",
    "postDate": "2014-07-09",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SwPsyUWvY1M?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Part 1 of 3</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.RADesigns.com\" target=\"_blank\">R.A.D. crew</a> assembled in California for a week of skateboarding up the coast. Featuring team riders Max Ballesteros, James Kelly, Cole Kurtz, Adam Persson, Louis Pilloni, Jimmy Riha, and Jackson Shapiera; the crew weaved their way down coastal mountain passes in search of perfect runs. In part 1, the crew made base camp at Skate House Media to skate a Malibu classic.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/05/21/2014/r-a-d-crew-adventures-california-coastal-mountains\" target=\"_blank\">Full R.A.D. Coast Adventures Trip Edit</a></p>",
