    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/32312353\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\n</p><p>Maryhill Freeride organizer and King Rat, Dean Ozan, is proud to bring you the The Maryhill Ratz Boarder-Cross.</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>In it’s third year, the Cathlamet Downhill Corral has grown to be one of the most unique and diverse events on the west coast. The 3 day event featured a downhill race, slide jam, slalom race, push race, and for the first time a boarder-cross.</p>\n<p>\n</p><p> Special thanks to the <a href=\"https://www.fivemilelongboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Five Mile</a> crew for building the ramps.</p>",
