    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/REM48cKM2H8?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Part 2 of 3</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.RADesigns.com\" target=\"_blank\">R.A.D.</a> crew assembled in California for a week of skateboarding up the coast. Featuring team riders <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/10/13/2014/r-a-d-influence-adam-persson-and-james-kelly\" target=\"_blank\">James Kelly</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/09/05/2014/rayne-longboards-presents-cole-kurtz-getting-savage-in-arizona\" target=\"_blank\">Cole Kurtz</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/10/14/2014/gullwing-truck-co-welcome-to-the-team-louis-pilloni\" target=\"_blank\">Louis Pilloni</a>, <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/11/18/2014/session-jimmy-riha\" target=\"_blank\">Jimmy Riha</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/04/05/2013/ride-to-action-with-duke-and-jacko\" target=\"_blank\">Jackson Shapiera</a>; the crew weaved their way down coastal mountain passes in search of perfect runs. In part 2, the crew made base camp in Santa Barbara to skate a desolate run tucked away in the mountains.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/11/10/2014/r-a-d-crew-adventures-california-coastal-mountains-part-1-malibu\" target=\"_blank\">R.A.D. Crew Adventures: Part 1 – Malibu</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/05/21/2014/r-a-d-crew-adventures-california-coastal-mountains\" target=\"_blank\">Full R.A.D. Coast Adventures Trip Edit</a></p>",
