    "pageTitle": "Skatesgiving: Vermont",
    "postDate": "2015-07-14",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/54097202\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>The Skatesgiving crew spent the first few days of the trip in Vermont dodging rain while <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/jake-palmer\">Jake Palmer</a> showed us around to all the good spots in the area. Be sure to check back every other Thursday for a new <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/skatesgiving\">Skatesgiving</a> video. Thanks to the sponsors for making all of this possible. <a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/home/\" target=\"_blank\">Comet</a>, <a href=\"https://www.sector9.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sector 9</a>, <a href=\"https://www.landyachtz.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Landyachtz</a>, &amp; Kebbek. Big thanks to <a href=\"https://vermontsessions.tumblr.com/\" target=\"_blank\">VTLBC</a> for the hospitality. </p>\n<p><b><span id=\"more-7588\"></span></b></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/scl6SIl_6cA\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>",
