    "pageTitle": "Comet Skateboards // Brucin’ USA (Part 2 of 3)",
    "postDate": "2013-04-09",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eOAw_mCssm0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com\" target=\"_blank\">Comet Skateboards</a> is proud to present the second of three Brucin’ USA Segments.  In part 2 Eric Jensen, Anthony Flis and Nick Ketner head first to Texas to hang with some good Texan folk on their way to ABQ for the legendary Ditch Slap. They are joined by Big Dave, Nick Ronzani and James Tracey in the Ditches of New Mexico for some more shredding. Lots of friendly faces and good times in Part 2. Stay tuned Next friday for Part 3!!</p>",
