    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/32624407\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>A good portion on the Skatehouse crew is on the East coast right now. Louis, Kody, and I are stuck in California’s winter at SkateHouse. We asked if we could join in with the east coasters for their epic skatesgiving trip, but our dreams were shot down prematurely. Their mission is to film and document some of the best east coast riders on the best east coast hills. No west coast riders allowed so don’t expect much. All jokes aside, check out this little clip they managed to upload mid tour. Keep posted to SkateHouse for the full Skatesgiving tour hitting an east coast computer near you soon. </p>",
