    "bodyText": "<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/6dBEg2jPdFw?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Thank you, Dalua Downhill fan. We got second place in the Netflix Contest with a great number of votes. This gives great visibility to our film. Many people discovered our film and skate downhill because of this election online. Rest assured that many doors will open in the future…Dalua Downhill was selected among 10 best brazilian independent films of the last 10 years to compete in a Netflix Prize (Prêmio Netflix). This is a video we made to promote the film.”</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"700\" height=\"525\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/3NNOwvjkefw?rel=0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></p>",
