    "bodyText": "<p>The <a href=\"https://www.bigmountainskate.com/events/knk-longboard-camp/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">KNK longboard camp</a> is a week long assembly of the european scene. Six days straight, two camps in a row. Every straphanger gets as many <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BXONIXgn9ur/?taken-by=kebbekskateboards\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bus</a> runs as they can take all day long. Kebbek Skateboards &amp; <a href=\"https://skatebloodorange.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Skate Blood Orange</a> enthusiast <a href=\"https://skatehousemedia.com/tags/emma-daigle\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Emma Daigle</a> attending to indulge in her apex hunting.</p>",
