    "pageTitle": "Skatesgiving Teaser Photo",
    "postDate": "2012-10-05",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/maxwellstoreydubler/6461385209/sizes/l/in/photostream/\"><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/skatesgiving-teaser-photo-skatehousemediacom/6461385209_15daa11902_b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"819\"></a></p>\n<p>As you probably know by now, the Skatehouse’s East Coast contingent recently went back east for a 10-day filming trip with some of the best riders from the right coast. We put in work, waking up before dawn, filming all day, and eating terrible southern food to bring you video and photos of the sickest hills nobody’s seen. We’re back now; so check back over the next few weeks for video episodes.</p>\n<p>Special thanks to the trip sponsors: Comet, Kebbek, Landyachtz, Rayne, Sector 9, and Rotule.</p>",
