    "pageTitle": "Session: Gotwood Pass in the Rocky State",
    "postDate": "2013-08-11",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<p><iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/55869412?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;badge=0&amp;color=9e0000\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\"></iframe></p>\n<p>After the memorable <a href=\"https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/buffalo-bill-2012\" target=\"_blank\">Buffalo Bill Downhill</a>, Colorado locals,<a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/team/justin-dubois\" target=\"_blank\"> Justin Dubois</a> of <a href=\"https://www.cometskateboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Comet</a> and <a href=\"https://madridskateboards.com/team/zak-maytum\" target=\"_blank\">Zak Maytum</a> of <a href=\"https://madridskateboards.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Madrid</a>, took the crew out to a place where the roads are big, fast, and open with plenty of gorgeous views you don’t want to get too close to.</p>",
    "tags": [],
    "categories": [
      "Road Trip",
      "Sessions"
    ],
    "contentUrls": [
      "https://www.skatehousemedia.com/tags/buffalo-bill-2012",
      "https://www.cometskateboards.com/team/justin-dubois",
      "https://www.cometskateboards.com",
      "https://madridskateboards.com/team/zak-maytum",
      "https://madridskateboards.com",
      "https://player.vimeo.com/video/55869412?title=0&byline=0&badge=0&color=9e0000"
    ],
    "ranking": 1,
