    "postDate": "2013-03-16",
    "author": "SkateHouseMedia",
    "bodyText": "<div id=\"body\">\n<p><a href=\"https://s437.photobucket.com/albums/qq92/Expectoration/?action=view&amp;current=Dipshit.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://assets.skatehousemedia.com/post-photos/happy-holidays/Dipshit.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Photobucket\"></a></p>\n<p>“Hey guys. I thought I would send you some pics of a crash I had while  not wearing a shirt. Bad times I always wear shirts now. You could post  em if you want…that would be cool. The pics are attached.<br>\nThanks for your time,<br>\nBryce Bookwalter<br>\nP.S. It happened in Albuquerque NM on the sidewalk beside the Indian School ditch.”</p>\n<p>The above picture was the least gruesome of the lot, we went ahead and threw in some holiday cheer</p>\n</div>",
